<item>
            <title>[LU-11244] &apos;make debs&apos; mistakenly ignores IB options</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11244</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If Lustre is compiled with &apos;--with-o2ib=no&apos; or similar options, and then do &apos;make debs&apos; will ignore the option mentioned above.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is in file &apos;debian/rules&apos; where IB options set to null string as &apos;IB_OPTIONS?=&quot;&quot;&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
